node.text:
Ethan + Katelynn’s (@thehuntersvanlife) self-converted, custom van. These guys have quite the story. They were tired of the 9-5 plus the rising housing costs in Nashville & decided to hit the road in 2018. They put in the money for a 2018 Ram Promaster & haven’t looked back! They’re both super creative, Ethan being a talented musician! Stick around ‘em to see what else they’ll be up to in the future. 🤙🏼

Thanks to @katyzientek for the inspiration!

node.text:
When you come across a rad couple putting everything in for a good cause, I gotta call ‘em out. Meet Seth & Emily Britt (@theboxhop), a creative couple near Logan, Ohio. Let me tell you guys, their heart + vision is so big, with a desire for focusing outwards towards others. I think we could all learn a thing or two from how they’ve taken a couple metal boxes & transformed them into THIS! 
Seth & Britt, any words y’all got for us? Comment them below. 👇🏼
Got questions for them? Drop ‘em below y’all. 
Till next time!

Photos by @theboxhop
